header_text: As you're finishing an assignment at midnight, you realize you still have a couple of tasks left. You plan to wake up a little early to finish them. While you're setting your alarm and thinking about your plan, you feel confident.

elements.Text: Are you anxious about your plan to finish your tasks in the morning?
